channel.title: The Remake Of 2012
channel.description:
Hello moparscape, I have started this project because im done playing pk/eco/spawn servers, and want back the time of 2012.
progress
Done 100% lodestone -----------> done [url=http://gyazo.com/e9929ebb11026eb5a28a296c837ab615]http://gyazo.com/e9929ebb11026eb5a28a296c837ab615[/url] 100% fishing guild -----------> done 100% mining guild -----------> done 90 % underground cockroaches at edge -----------> done (2 levels) 100% greens (PK) -----------> done 100% hill giants -----------> done 100% babarian / gnome course -----------> done 100% from falador to blue dragons -----------> done 95 % combad No alching YET. -----------> done 85 % gamersgrotto (red, white, purple portal's work -----------> done 100% slayer tower -----------> done 100 % pickable (flax, patatoe's etc) -----------> done 75% % firemaking (logs till magic) even ivy -----------> done and bone fire 100% prayers, lunar, ancient ----------->done
Good combad Perfect switching. fixed some locations
its very basic atm , started this project today
i can use some good developers, add me on skype if interested about joining me. danny.overesch
more pics, info , more, comming next week
Gr Danny
